'''Headwater of Bisotun''' is a historical [[Headwater]] which located in the Ancient site of [[Bisotun]] city in [[Kermanshah Province]] of [[Iran]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Files of registration of Iranian national heritages|url=http://iranshahrpedia.ir/static/view/page/cultural-heritage-reports|website=Archive of Cultural Heritage, Handicrafts and Tourism Organization of Iran|language=en|deadurl=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023092637/http://iranshahrpedia.ir/static/view/page/cultural-heritage-reports|archivedate=2015-10-23|df=}}</ref> this Headwater listed in Iranian national heritages list on March 16th 2002. it also listed as Iranian national natural heritages on July 25th 2009. Headwater of Bisotun also irrigates nearby farms.<ref>[http://www.tebyan.net/newindex.aspx?pid=18790 معرفی سراب‌های استان کرمانشاه ] تبیان نت</ref>
