{{Italic title}} '''''Pathogens and Global Health''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] published by [[Maney Publishing]]. It covers [[tropical disease]]s, including their [[microbiology]], [[epidemiology]] and [[molecular biology]], as well as [[medical entomology]], [[HIV/AIDS]], [[malaria]], and [[tuberculosis]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Andrea Crisanti (scientist)|Andrea Crisanti]] ([[Imperial College London]]).
==History== The journal was established by Sir [[Ronald Ross]] in 1906 as ''Annals of Tropical Medicine and Parasitology'' to share the results of the [[Liverpool School of Tropical Medicine]]'s research and field expeditions. In May 2011, the journal was purchased by Maney Publishing, obtaining its current title in 2012, reflecting a broader focus including the [[biology]], [[immunology]], [[genetics]], treatment, and control of [[pathogens]] of medical relevance beyond a regional definition.
==Abstracting and indexing== The journal is abstracted and indexed in: {{columns-list|colwidth=30em| *[[AGRICOLA]] *[[BIOSIS Previews]]<ref name=ISI/> *[[CAB Abstracts]] *[[Chemical Abstracts]] *[[Current Contents]]/Clinical Medicine<ref name=ISI>{{cite web |url=http://ip-science.thomsonreuters.com/mjl/ |title=Master Journal List |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |work=Intellectual Property & Science |accessdate=2015-03-22}}</ref> *Current Contents/Life Sciences<ref name=ISI/> *[[Elsevier BIOBASE]]/[[Current Awareness in Biological Sciences]] *[[EMBASE|EMBASE/Excerpta Medica]] *[[Index Medicus]]/[[MEDLINE]]/[[PubMed]]<ref name=MEDLINE>{{cite web |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog/101583421 |title=Pathogens and Global Health |work=NLM Catalog |publisher=[[National Center for Biotechnology Information]] |accessdate=2015-03-22}}</ref> *[[PASCAL (database)|PASCAL]] *[[Science Citation Index]]<ref name=ISI/> *[[Scopus]]<ref name=Scopus>{{cite web |url=http://www.elsevier.com/online-tools/scopus/content-overview |title=Content overview |publisher=[[Elsevier]] |work=Scopus |accessdate=2015-03-22}}</ref> *[[Tropical Diseases Bulletin]] *[[The Zoological Record]]<ref name=ISI/> }} According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2014 [[impact factor]] of 1.656.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2015 |chapter=Pathogens and Global Health |title=2014 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]]}}</ref>
==References== {{Reflist}}
==External links== *{{Official website|http://www.maneyonline.com/loi/pgh}} *Print: {{ISSN|2047-7724}} *Online: {{ISSN|2047-7732}} *''Annals of Tropical Medicine and Parasitology'': {{ISSN|0003-4983}}
